              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11197291/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3447369/" class=" " title="不卖大蒜">不卖大蒜</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11197291">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">对比现实，会有更好的理解。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-02-08 18:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                对比现实，会有更好的理解。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
